OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early low cloud quickly
OL,6,Fclearing to leave a dry morning, with
OL,7,Fprolonged spells of sunshine
OL,8,Fdeveloping quite widely. A hot
OL,9,Fafternoon to come, with light winds
OL,10,Facross the region and plenty of hazy
OL,11,Fsunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FPlenty of sunshine to end the
OL,14,Fday, though an isolated shower may
OL,15,Fdevelop towards the south coast. Dry
OL,16,Fovernight, with clear skies for most.
OL,17,FTemperatures remaining on the warm
OL,18,Fside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
