OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAny morning cloud clearing to
OL,6,Fleave another dry and sunny day. The
OL,7,Fsunshine turning hazy at times in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Remaining hot, though a
OL,9,Flittle cooler along some coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,12,Fmostly dry into the weekend, with
OL,13,Fsunny spells. A few isolated late
OL,14,Fafternoon showers remain possible.
OL,15,FTemperatures trending a little nearer
OL,16,Fto average, but still feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
